		<description><![CDATA[“How much for the cowboy in the window?”]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="1200" height="800" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Klassen_Buddy_0.jpg" class="webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image" alt="Illustration of a light pink couch with two cushions and a white blanket draped over the top." loading="lazy" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; clear:both;max-width: 100%;" link_thumbnail="" srcset="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Klassen_Buddy_0.jpg 1200w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Klassen_Buddy_0-735x490.jpg 735w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Klassen_Buddy_0-348x232.jpg 348w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><style>
